  <entry>
    <title>MMD 靜畫 | 每月 23 文之日（2022.12）</title>
    <link href="https://copy-alcide.github.io/MMDPic/2022/MMDPic-20221223/"/>
    <id>https://copy-alcide.github.io/MMDPic/2022/MMDPic-20221223/</id>
    <published>2022-12-23T00:36:43.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-12-23T00:51:23.926Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage/main/Aya_20221223.png&default=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage/main/Aya_20221223.png"></p><p>每月文圖已經快成爲防止技能生疏而做的了，最近各種意義上都確實有些忙。</p><p>這次是想做成手擋陽光的姿勢，但是加上直射的光源之後指節部分的陰影就變得有點看不到了，就跟手伸直着一樣。明年有時間了還是要好好看看 AbsoluteShadow 之類的工具怎麼用，渲染技術也得提高些。</p><p>這次就不到處發圖了。</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Text</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">借物表</span><br><span class="line">模型：</span><br><span class="line">宝改 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project　射命丸文改変モデル</span><br><span class="line">mato.sus304 OPTLETデジタル一眼レフカメラセット_v0.8</span><br><span class="line">追憶の機械人形 ヤツメウナギの蒲焼き</span><br><span class="line">キャベツ鉢 串団子3種類ver1.0</span><br><span class="line">鯖缶 人里</span><br><span class="line">渲染：</span><br><span class="line">Ray-MMD by Rui</span><br><span class="line">dPostPointLight_v1.00 by 極北P</span><br><span class="line">面光源エフェクト PanelLight by そぼろ</span><br><span class="line">ikBokeh_v020a by ikeno</span><br><span class="line">MikuMikuEffect用ディフュージョンフィルタ by そぼろ</span><br><span class="line">Toon_RC by RedialC</span><br><span class="line">RayMMD用のマテリアル24種類 by 世界最弱のサーモントラウト</span><br><span class="line">軟件：</span><br><span class="line">MMM ver 1.2.9.2</span><br><span class="line">MMD ver 9.26</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage/main/Aya_20221223.png&amp;default=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage/main/Aya_20221223.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;每月文圖已經快成爲防止技能生疏而做的了，最近各種意義上都確實有些忙。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;這次是想做成手擋陽光的姿勢，但是加上直射的光源之後指節部分的陰影就變得有點看不到了，就跟手伸直着一樣。明年有時間了還是要好好看看 AbsoluteShadow 之類的工具怎麼用，渲染技術也得提高些。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;這次就不到處發圖了。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
