    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage/main/Aya_20221123.png&default=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage/main/Aya_20221123.png"></p><p>又是每個月的文之日圖。</p><p>雖然上次說要調整暗處過暗的問題，這次相機機身和柱子快要分不清似乎是真沒什麼辦法了，就連不加渲染的情況下都不怎麼看得出。</p><p>不論如何至少是嘗試了。</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Text</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">借物表</span><br><span class="line">模型：</span><br><span class="line">宝改 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project　射命丸文改変モデル</span><br><span class="line">mato.sus304 OPTLETデジタル一眼レフカメラセット_v0.8</span><br><span class="line">鯖缶 人里</span><br><span class="line">渲染：</span><br><span class="line">Ray-MMD by Rui</span><br><span class="line">dPostPointLight_v1.00 by 極北P</span><br><span class="line">面光源エフェクト PanelLight by そぼろ</span><br><span class="line">ikBokeh_v020a by ikeno</span><br><span class="line">MikuMikuEffect用ディフュージョンフィルタ by そぼろ</span><br><span class="line">Toon_RC by RedialC</span><br><span class="line">RayMMD用のマテリアル24種類 by 世界最弱のサーモントラウト</span><br><span class="line">軟件：</span><br><span class="line">MMM ver 1.2.9.2</span><br><span class="line">MMD ver 9.26</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage/main/Aya_20221123.png&amp;default=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage/main/Aya_20221123.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;又是每個月的文之日圖。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;雖然上次說要調整暗處過暗的問題，這次相機機身和柱子快要分不清似乎是真沒什麼辦法了，就連不加渲染的情況下都不怎麼看得出。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;不論如何至少是嘗試了。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
